@aperture#160532 Zadatak je da gradimo neprunano stablo, odnosno ovisi o datasetu koliko ce biti duboko. Partition ti radim znaci ovako: 

```cpp
tuple<Data, Data> Calculations::partition(const Data& data, const Question& q) {
  Data true_rows;
  Data false_rows;

  for (const auto &row: data) {
    if (q.solve(row))
      true_rows.push_back(row);
    else
      false_rows.push_back(row);
  }

  return forward_as_tuple(true_rows, false_rows);
}
```

